    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Valence Bond Theory (VBT)</h1>
            <p>Understanding Chemical Bonding for College Students</p>
        </header>

        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="index.html">What is Chemistry?</a></li>
                <li><a href="coordination-compounds.html">Coordination Compounds</a></li>
                <li><a href="vbt-theory.html" class="active">Valence Bond Theory</a></li>
